# Project hub

Open **`AGENTS.md`** at the repository root before large changes. It maps components (`src/api`, `src/runner`, `k8s`, etc.), lists migration and deploy commands, and points to READMEs and scoped rules under `.cursor/rules/`. For shell commands that need tools from **`devenv.nix`**, follow **`devenv-shell.mdc`** (`devenv shell -- …` from repo root).

Match conventions for the paths you edit; avoid scope creep beyond the user’s task.

If the change establishes new invariants (architecture, how to run things, or agent-facing conventions), update **`AGENTS.md`** and/or the relevant **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** in the same change—see the **Maintenance** section in `AGENTS.md`.
